OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FThe Football Association's Chief
OL,8,FExecutive, Mark Bullingham, said
OL,9,FEngland Manager Tuchel is doing 'a
OL,10,Fbrilliant job'
OL,12,FHead coach Thomas Tuchel has moved
OL,13,FEngland to the next level, according
OL,14,Fto his boss, Mark Bullingham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of the Three Lions'
OL,8,Fopening World Cup group game against
OL,9,FCroatia, the Football Association's
OL,10,F(FA) Chief Executive said: "Gareth
OL,11,F(Southgate) built a brilliant
OL,12,Fplatform, brilliant foundations that
OL,13,Fhe (Tuchel) has been able to build on.
OL,15,F"He's got high standards, he's got
OL,16,Fbrilliant energy and he's created this
OL,17,Fband of brothers. We believe we've got
OL,18,Fa world-class coach who's really in
OL,19,Fthe zone and doing a brilliant job."
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@ApmsD@KpnuD@DpmuD@Kpn{D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,F"I think the collective strength of
OL,8,Fthe team is phenomenal. I think
OL,9,Fthey've really, really come together
OL,10,Fand we feel like we're in as good a
OL,11,Fposition as we can be."
OL,13,FTuchel was originally brought in by
OL,14,FBullingham on a short-term, 18-month
OL,15,Fdeal, specifically to win this
OL,16,Ftournament.
OL,18,FSince then, his contract has been
OL,19,Fextended. Why though, given the German
OL,20,Fhasn't really proved himself yet on
OL,21,Fthe international stage?
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,F"He qualified for the tournament
OL,8,Fwithout conceding a goal and broke
OL,9,Frecords in the process of doing that."
OL,11,FBullingham almost bristles at the
OL,12,Fsuggestion the extension wasn't
OL,13,Fjustified.
OL,15,F"From our point of view, we don't look
OL,16,Fat tournaments on a standalone basis,
OL,17,Fwe're planning for 2028. We had a
OL,18,Fmanager in place who was doing a great
OL,19,Fjob, and he was prepared to carry on
OL,20,Fwith us, which is great."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@fO]wD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FThe one thing an England head coach at
OL,8,Fa major tournament can guarantee is
OL,9,Fflak from all sides, especially if it
OL,10,Fstarts to go wrong.
OL,12,FHow does Bullingham think Tuchel will
OL,13,Fdeal with that scrutiny? No problem,
OL,14,Fis the answer.
OL,16,F"I think it would be absolutely fine.
OL,17,FI think he's obviously managed at a
OL,18,Fvery high level, won the Champions
OL,19,FLeague and so on.''
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FThe build-up to this World Cup has
OL,8,Fbeen littered with controversy, none
OL,9,Fbigger than the cost of tickets for
OL,10,Fordinary fans.
OL,12,FWhile the FA recognises that many have
OL,13,Fbeen priced out, its most loyal
OL,14,Ftravelling supporters they believe
OL,15,Fwill be there in numbers, thanks to
OL,16,FFifa's decision to release a cheap
OL,17,Fcategory ticket.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,F"We were really pleased with the move
OL,8,Fthat FIFA made to create the new
OL,9,Fcategory for $60. All our fans are
OL,10,Fimportant but the most important are
OL,11,Fthose that follow us on the road
OL,12,Fthrough thick and thin. And the group
OL,13,Ffollowing us for the last four years,
OL,14,Fmost of them are going to be here and
OL,15,Fmost of them will be supporting the
OL,16,Fteam."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FHydration breaks are something that
OL,8,Fwill impact every game in this
OL,9,Ftournament. Some say it's sensible to
OL,10,Fprotect player welfare, others are
OL,11,Fmore cynical, suggesting it's simply
OL,12,FFifa's device to allow commercial
OL,13,Fnetworks to squeeze in more adverts
OL,14,Fduring matches.
OL,16,FBullingham, who is hoping to be part
OL,17,Fof staging a home nations Women's
OL,18,FWorld Cup in 2035, does not believe
OL,19,Fthese breaks will formally become a
OL,20,Fpart of every game from this
OL,21,Ftournament on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FIn other words, the suspicion is that
OL,8,Feven in the lower temperatures in the
OL,9,FUK, Fifa will pause matches to
OL,10,Fcapitalise on that ad-break
OL,11,Fopportunity.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,F"That's not the way we're seeing it.
OL,8,FWe're seeing it as a tournament-
OL,9,Fspecific move. For them (Fifa) to
OL,10,Fbring it in at the beginning, and for
OL,11,Fit to be consistent throughout the
OL,12,Fwhole tournament is sensible."
OL,14,FMany England players from both the
OL,15,Fmen's and women's teams have been
OL,16,Ftargeted by racist abuse online during
OL,17,Frecent tournaments, and Bullingham
OL,18,Fsays the FA is working hard to protect
OL,19,Fthem.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@YpmqD@^pntD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,FWhile he's hoping none of Tuchel's men
OL,8,Fwill be singled out in the coming
OL,9,Fweeks, he says they'll be ready if it
OL,10,Fdoes happen.
OL,12,F"In the last few tournaments, we've
OL,13,Fworked with agencies to develop all of
OL,14,Fthe information to allow prosecutions
OL,15,Fto happen and now we're even funding
OL,16,Fthe police, we work very closely with
OL,17,Fthem. We've seen progress in terms of
OL,18,Fprosecutions.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781621296
OL,3,CFA boss on Tuchel, Fifa's rampant
OL,4,Ccommercialism and tackling online
OL,5,Cracists
OL,7,F"This is not a victimless crime.
OL,8,FPeople who perpetrate hate crime will
OL,9,Fbe punished for it and we will make
OL,10,Fsure they're brought to justice."
OL,12,FBut are the social media companies
OL,13,Fworking as hard to protect the players?
OL,15,F" I think there's more they should be
OL,16,Fdoing. I think they've done a better
OL,17,Fjob at taking down some of the
OL,18,Fmaterial when it goes up, but I don't
OL,19,Fthink they've done enough to prevent
OL,20,Fit, and we'd like them to do more."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]wD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
